item.title: Good ways too make some cash
item.dc:creator: @vader_killer vader killer
item.description:
@vader_killer wrote:

Hi,

Do either one of these 3 options:

  1. make a noob accout, add ‘boxbreaker2’ to moparsironminerbanker. Then run it for ahwhile (good few hours). Next get all the iron it mined & put it on ur main then sell it. Continue this until he can guildmine.

  2. Do the first step & you can guildmine after ahwhile or just use an account that can already guildmine. This second step is to get stupid3ooo’s guildminer banker, add boxbreaker2 into it also. Use this just like the last step & every time you finish running it put all the coal onto ur main. Easy money.

  3. Get moparswillowcutterbanker & add the boxbreaker 2 & *pwnd’s axeheadfinder into it. Then run it in draynor village until u get huge amounts of willows. Then put them onto ur main &sell them.

There is many more ways to get money from scar but there’s 3 of them (the obious one’s :p)

No worry’s dud. Vader killer

*note: do not ask me where to get pwnd’s axehead finder.
